00:42:57,300 --> 00:42:58,160
to mail it over?

1187
00:42:58,190 --> 00:42:59,270
What if they don't like it?

1188
00:42:59,270 --> 00:43:00,020
Why bother?

1189
00:43:00,200 --> 00:43:00,950
It shows

1190
00:43:00,980 --> 00:43:01,980
that we care.

1191
00:43:02,940 --> 00:43:05,100
You can't get this hardcover edition

1192
00:43:05,200 --> 00:43:07,600
of the Four Great Classical Novels abroad.

1193
00:43:07,860 --> 00:43:08,880
I'm going out for a bit.
